Install (just one step):

    python2 setup.py install --prefix=/usr

To start mpy, run:

    mpy

Main configuration file is /etc/mpy.conf
Configuration sample is /usr/share/mpy/mpy.conf.example
Edit and copy it to /etc/mpy.conf
And you can also create a user-scope configuration file ~/.mpy/mpy.conf

Default lyrics directory is ~/.mpy/lyrics

Enjoy!
